msgid "The FIDE rules stipulate that only the pairings of the round <b>prior</b> to the current one may be modified. Changes to pairings previous to this should be made at the <b>end</b> of the tournament, <b>after</b> the rankings have been published, and solely for the computation of the FIDE ratings."
